<h6 class="kicker"><a href="//dealbook.blogs.nytimes.com/category/legal/">LEGAL/REGULATORY Â»</a></h6>
<div class="ru-story">
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><span class="title">Did the Bank Bailout Do Enough for the Country? <span class="divider">Â |Â </span></span><!-- end .title --> Room for Debate asks: Did the government miss a historic opportunity to reshape the financial system â or was its moderate approach correct? <span class="elsewhere"><a href="//www.nytimes.com/roomfordebate/2014/05/20/did-the-bank-bailout-do-enough-for-the-country"> NEW YORK TIMES </a></span></p>
